=Price=
When bought from the Indigo Plateau / Pokémon League, the price for Protein rises irreversibly, similar to [[Pokéballs|Masterballs]]. It starts off at 10,000 {{pdollar}}, increments by a factor of 1.1 every purchase, and caps at 1,000,000 {{pdollar}} after 49 purchases.
